videos.description: Nick Richards throws down the ferocious dunk that gets the Kentucky crowd on their feet.
videos.headline: Richards throws down authoritative slam

videos.description: Ashton Hagans fakes out the Florida defense as he finds his way to a wide-open basket late in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Florida forgets to play defense on Kentucky basket) 2020/2/22

videos.headline: Florida forgets to play defense on Kentucky basket

videos.description: Florida's Ques Glover hits the 3-point shot with 0.4 seconds left as Florida ties the game 31-31 at halftime.
videos.headline: Florida ties game at buzzer

videos.description: Immanuel Quickley gets Dick Vitale excited with a big and-1 layup early in the second half.
videos.headline: Quickley hits big and-1 basket

videos.description: Immanuel Quickley gets the lucky bounce to fall on a long 3-pointer late in the second half.
videos.headline: Quickley gets lucky bounce on 3

videos.description: In the waning seconds, Florida's attempted layup is blocked and the Gators turn the ball over to Kentucky on their final possession of the game.
videos.headline: Florida botches their final possession
